HEADWORD: Asinine
<hw>As"i*nine</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>asininus</ets>, fr. <ets>asinus</ets> ass. See <er>Ass</er>.]</ety>
